<div class="card" style="max-width:800px;margin:auto;">
    <h2 class="page-title">Help & Support</h2>

    <p>Find answers to common questions about using the Library Management System.</p>

    <hr/>

    <h3>📌 How to login?</h3>
    <p>Go to Login page, select Admin or Student mode, enter your email and password, then click login.</p>

    <h3>📌 How to issue a book?</h3>
    <p>Login → Go to Books → Select a book → Click "Issue".</p>

    <h3>📌 How to return a book?</h3>
    <p>Go to Transactions → Find your issued book → Click "Return".</p>

    <h3>📌 What if I forget my password?</h3>
    <p>Contact admin or use the Contact Us page to request password reset.</p>

    <h3>📌 How to check available books?</h3>
    <p>Go to Books section and use search or filters to find books.</p>

    <h3>📌 Who can add or remove books?</h3>
    <p>Only Admin users have permission to manage books and students.</p>

</div>
 
